.MARINE...
(Today through Monday)
Issued at 849 AM PDT Wed Mar 25 2026

Northerly breezes will become strong to near gale this afternoon
and evening, which will bring widespread hazardous conditions.
Gale force gusts will occur across the inner waters and outer
waters with bays experiencing conditions hazardous to small craft.
Seas will build to become rough to very rough as a result.
Conditions will slowly improve Friday and into the weekend with
moderate northerly breezes and moderate seas.

